info.title: Household
info.description: This is intended to be a 1 stop shop for our customers to order reports. They will sign up for a group of reports, send in a single request and get a group of reports back. This is to make it easier instead of calling each API separately.

200.description:
Success

Upon successful call, the service will return a 200 response along with the data requested. No hits will return an empty body with http status 200.
